%% 3.1.15 Reports — sequence (layered)
%% Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database
%% Placeholder API: POST /api/Reports/revenue-export hoặc tương đương — implement sau

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (/reports)
    participant RC as Controller (ReportsController — future)
    participant RS as Service (ReportExportService — future)
    participant Repo as Repository (Order Payment aggregates)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Open Reports tab e.g. Revenue
    Actor->>UI: Select month, format Excel, Generate Report

    UI->>UI: Validate date range ≤ 2 years (BR15)

    UI->>RC: POST /api/Reports/Generate (month, format, year)
    RC->>RS: BuildRevenueReportAsync(range)
    RS->>RS: Check range span ≤ 2 years else 400
    RS->>Repo: Aggregate revenue from Orders / Payments
    Repo->>DB: SELECT (heavy)
    DB-->>Repo: aggregates
    RS->>RS: Render Excel/PDF buffer
    RS-->>RC: File bytes + filename
    RC-->>UI: 200 application/octet-stream or file URL
    UI-->>Actor: Download BaoCao_T9_FaceRide.xlsx

    Note over Actor,DB: BR15 — từ chối export nếu from/to vượt 2 năm liên tiếp; tối ưu query/paging nội bộ.
